OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FApart from
OL,6,Fthe odd shower it will be a dry
OL,7,Fevening with some late sunshine.
OL,8,FOvernight cloud will tend to increase
OL,9,Fwith outbreaks of rain arriving
OL,10,Fthrough the early hours in the west,
OL,11,Faffecting most by dawn. Breeze also
OL,12,Ffreshening.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FAny early brightness quickly
OL,15,Freplaced by a band of rain which will
OL,16,Fspread eastwards throughout the
OL,17,Fmorning. The rain will be heavy at
OL,18,Ftimes, giving a rather wet afternoon.
OL,19,FBreezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
