OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FRather
OL,6,Fchangeable throughout the period with
OL,7,Fa mix of sunshine and heavy, thundery
OL,8,Fshowers interspersed with a longer
OL,9,Fspell of rain on Wednesday.
OL,10,FTemperatures near average for early
OL,11,FJune.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
